modDescription:
A cork hat from Australia. This mod adds the cork [hat](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-clothing/) Adreden made for JaWoodle. JaWoodle has had it in his DoomsDay series on YouTube.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/adredengaming/adreden_modlets/-/archive/master/adreden_modlets-master.zip?path=DredWoodles_CorkHat)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/16328-adredens-modlets/).
